                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6886" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0158</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8399 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">链中有数，信息无阻：AL公司供应链数字化转型的探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Data in the Supply Chain，Information Unimpeded: The Exploration of Digital Transformation of AL’s Supply </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈金涛，吕思齐，仝飞飞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春爱尔铃克铃尔有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链数字化转型；供应链管理；供应链整合；汽车零部件企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation of supply chain; Supply chain management; Supply chain integration; Automobile parts enterprise</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了AL公司自2019年在供应链管理方面存在的问题及解决思路。阐明了AL公司内部人员的信息沟通存在偏差、信息的传递存在滞后性以及信息的存储与交互方式效率较低等问题，并对问题进行梳理讨论。从转型前准备、转型计划与转型实施视角阐明了企业供应链数字化转型的方案及实施路径，使公司供应链管理绩效得到了快速提高。本案例可以引导学员思考在大数据、互联网、云计算技术条件下，供应链管理的走向及供应链数字化转型对企业的重大影响，并结合所掌握的知识深入剖析供应链数字化成功实施的必备因素，进而引导学员建立数字化供应链的思维。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the problems found by AL company in supply chain management since 2019, and expounds the problems such as the deviation in the information communication of the personnel , the lag in the transmission of information and the low efficiency of the storage and exchange of information within the AL company, etc. And this paper discusses the problems and puts forward the scheme and implementation path of the preparation before the transformation, the plan of the transformation and the implementation path of the digital transformation of the supply chain, so as to improve the performance of supply chain data management. This case can lead the students to think about the development direction of supply chain management under the condition of big data ,the Internet, and cloud computing, and the important influence of data on supply chain management. and combined with the knowledge in-depth analysis of the necessary factors for the successful implementation of supply chain digitization, and then guide students to establish the thinking of digital supply chain.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数字化供应链》、《运营与供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业数字化；供应链数字化；传统供应链管理；供应链数字化转型意义；供应链整合；供应链整合对实施供应链数字化的意义；供应链数字化转型与企业数字化转型的区别；供应链数字化转型动因；成功实施供应链数字化的关键要素；实施供应链数字化的策略；牛鞭效应；供应链数字化发展方向</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
